  "industry_note": "Borosilicate Glass (Type I/III, Pyrex 7740 / Schott Duran 8330 / KS B0801). 80% SiO₂ + 13% B₂O₃ + 4% Na₂O + 3% Al₂O₃. CTE 3.3×10⁻⁶/K (soda-lime 9 의 1/3 — thermal shock 우수, 100°C ΔT 견딤). σf 70 (flexural) / E 64 / ρ 2.23 / Tmax 500°C continuous, 800°C short. Refractive 1.474. 실험실 beaker, 화학 reactor, 가정 ovenware (Pyrex 'casserole'), 광학 (BK7 = 광 grade), 약병 (Type I borosilicate 약전 표준)."
